comment: Interesting movements on this one﹐ nice route!
For me the finish was really hard. I planted a firm left foot in the crack﹐ leaned right﹐ and stepped very high with the right.
Very height dependent. Jumping and holding the swing is V7﹐ but reaching and grabbing is V5.
Nice long route that requires some thought and planning
Really sick route! Great fun figuring out feet.
